I really think that this is more like a three-and-a-half-star production. While all attractive--especially Charlie Laine and the Genie herself, Tanya James--as a whole, the women mostly aren't my cup of tea. If you're into women with small natural breasts, you'll probably love it--everyone here fits that description.

It gets a rating this high from me primarily because of the sheer volume of explicit nudity--pretty unusual for a Peach release. And it actually is shot beautifully in parts, with great scenery.

I saw previews of this DVD on other Peach videos I own, and recently, I found it on "amazon.com". Celeste Star is my favorite girl on it, and it has her sexiest scenes, so it's a MUST HAVE DVD for me. I like Asian girls, so I certainly noticed Luana Lani. Covergirl Tanya James is attractive too as the Genie. I know what my wish would be, if I ever met such a Genie, and I'm sure many men agree with me. Charlie Laine has an intense scene that is my favorite of hers. Lacie Heart isn't bad, but I watch the girls listed first. With so many sexy girls in such sexy scenes, this is one of the best Peach DVDs to me. I own many of them, so take my word for it.

Just like the title says, it was a somewhat decent showing of some nice girls, but the dialogue sounds like it was some college kids drunken fantasy. There were not nearly enough girl on girl action scenes, and what little plot there was dissolved entirely near the end. A risky purchase at best.
